                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880625-67-off296 t17880625-67-cd297"></join>, a cotton handkerchief, value 10 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17880625-67-victim559" type="victimName">
                  Esau 
                  Harris
               <interp inst="t17880625-67-victim559" type="surname" value="Harris"></interp>
